com.aevi.payment

Class TransactionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aevi.helpers.BundleWrapper
      • com.aevi.payment.TransactionResult

  • public class TransactionResult
extends BundleWrapper
    Returned by the payment application after a transaction has been completed. It can be obtained in the onActivityResult handler using the fromIntent(Intent) method. 

     
 protected void onActivityResult(int requestCode, int resultCode, Intent data)
 {
 // Get transaction result
 TransactionResult result = TransactionResult.fromIntent(data);

  // Check whether the transaction was successful
  if (result.getTransactionStatus()==TransactionStatus.APPROVED)
    {
    // transaction successful
    } else {
    // transaction failed
    }
 }
    See Also:
    PaymentRequest, RefundRequest

        public TransactionReferences getTransactionReferences()

      • fromIntent

        public static TransactionResult fromIntent(android.content.Intent intent)
                                    throws AeviRequestDataMissingException
        Obtains a TransactionResult from an intent. If the intent is null or does not contain a transaction result, a AeviRequestDataMissingException is thrown.
        Parameters:
